reviewText: I'm not sure when this was taped, but as another reviewer said, it is the same jokes as in other specials. I love Katt Williams and watch the DVDs over and over. So you can imagine how upset I was to be able to say the jokes right along with him. I thought this was new material.  I was wrong.
Watch this only if you want to hear the same jokes Katt Williams has been telling for years...just changing the city names and his wardrobe. Not worth even a penny.
He definitely knows how to make people laugh.
